<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>myTamilDate Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7e9ff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            display: block;
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff713f;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text {
            color: #4a4a4a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .link {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .image-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .image-container>p {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: small;
            font-weight: 600;

            a {
                color: #2563eb;
            }
        }

        .image-container>img {
            width: 12rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer p:first-child>a {
            color: #d0a0ff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer p>a {
            color: #c8b0d0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img height="57px" width="174x"  src="<%= logo %>" alt="myTamilDate Logo" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="title">You can access your myTamilDate account soon!</h1>
        <p class="text">Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p class="text">
            Thanks for requesting to join the myTamilDate community! We're reviewing your account and will get back to
            you within 24 hours. Your account will be hidden until it's approved.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text">Why do we review accounts?</h2>
        <p class="text">
            To create a positive experience for all members, we require everyone to have real and complete profiles at
            all times.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text">Requirements for account approval</h2>
        <ul class="text">
            <li>Post real, high-quality images of yourself</li>
            <li>Complete all sections of your profile</li>
            <li>Adhere to our terms of use</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="<%= couple %>" alt="Couple" />
            <p>
                Shana & Ramesh met on <a href="<%= link %>" >mytamildate.com</a>. <a href="https://tamilculture.com/how-france-met-canada-a-mytamildatecom-love-story">Read their story here.</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
